1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T01:46:23.000Z","msg":"呢條柒婆幾時仆街"},{"pid":"914724257f2bb9f888ec59bd85617f600fd862d4","tid":1564704,"uid":2521,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T01:46:29.000Z","msg":"若能渡過危機，會進行大改革？<br />\nOn9仲要講出口當人人都on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你過到骨就唔會改啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家明係你班人錯，死不悔改<br />\n俾你過左骨，就即刻解決晒提出問題嘅人啦"},{"pid":"9a534c575237e8eeb7f7cb80fbae7d8290d92dc7","tid":1564704,"uid":290818,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T01:46:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T6rwNiz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT6rwNiz.jpg&h=9ece1703&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8f1a46c25561668c8214d1fc2493e55882838783","tid":1564704,"uid":199438,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T01:46:58.000Z","msg":"算罷啦<br />\n真香港人唔會再肯食朱古力味嘅屎"},{"pid":"a8811d5d6d28f7f43fcf02bfa9fbc3fefdbead22","tid":1564704,"uid":136216,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T01:47:10.000Z","msg":"根本佢現在是過街老鼠&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"8915567011f936ed9ac9e795fad9b79209764619","tid":1564704,"uid":65981,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3e4944e152256cc0e7b09eaabd04e4db7a85313e","tid":1564704,"uid":76702,"like":2,"dislike":41,"score":-39,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T01:16:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T01:47:34.000Z","msg":"屌你收嗲啦五毛狗 又帶風向"},{"pid":"6c54b35a98f297bea90f29a935b25064812fef1a","tid":1564704,"uid":12554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T01:47:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190913/large/1568308886_2323.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190913%2Flarge%2F1568308886_2323.jpg&h=43388a12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《路透社》早前流出林鄭月娥與商界閉門會議的錄音，揭示林鄭指自己如有選擇，會第一時間辭職及作出道歉後，早前《蘋果》亦報道林鄭席間也承認低估市民對中央的恐懼，又指14億內地人對反修訂《逃犯條例》事件有看法。《路透社》今天再將當日會談原文直錄，林鄭席間還大談特區政府應對反送中運動上的困難。<span style=\"color: red;\">林鄭當時提到，宣傳工作為港府最薄弱一環（I dare not say government carries out propaganda, but at least in terms of dissemination of factual information we are very, very weak），稱若能度過言這場危機，必須進行大改革，為繼任人營造較好管治環境，又自爆有國際公關為免被拖累名聲而請特區政府食檸檬。</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n即係加強資訊管制<br />\n修例去增加對人民嘅控制<br />\n同清算教育界/傳媒"},{"pid":"44db5d48087538105eaf9c5354073c1c453152e6","tid":1564704,"uid":9049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T01:47:53.000Z","msg":"Push <br />\n@期望連仔幫手壓制fake news <br />\n@上連登要用多用腦！<br />\n最新活動：唱民主聖歌，傳福音！<br />\n杯葛黨鐵商場：齋睇唔買，儲多d錢！<br />\n913中秋賞燈晚會，附近連儂牆見！<br />\n連儂牆戰線不能倒！修建連儂，有你有我<br />\n<ins>考驗毅力與堅持</ins><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: red;\">做更具價值嘅野</span><br />\n<br />\n#離開同溫層，接觸各種人，理解佢地嘅想法，將不支持我們的人轉為支持我們！這是成功的方法！<br />\n<br />\n@Template@<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />抗爭/革命搞十年八載唔出奇<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">衛城革命，生活抗爭；拖垮邪惡、打倒腐敗；</span><br />\n<em>每日任務：</em><br />\n1. 優先<span style=\"color: red;\">幫襯</span>良心商店<br />\n2. <span style=\"color: red;\">抵制</span>「邪惡」「無良」的商戶，例如cctvb廣告、黨鐵商埸、黑社會、打壓員工的店鋪，減少淘寶、減少八達通<br />\n3. 安全之下，<span style=\"color: red;\">免費港鐵</span>；二人同遊，一人免費；買平飛；長者八達通<br />\n4. 夜晚<span style=\"color: red;\">十點咆哮</span>！（改9點會少好多人）<br />\n5. <span style=\"color: red;\">健身+運動</span>，身體健康，鬥長命<br />\n6. <span style=\"color: red;\">每日一post</span>，社交媒體戰（Twitter, IG, Facebook, Reddit) #HongKongProtest #Chinazi<br />\n#FreeHongKong #HongKongProtests <br />\nTwitter 共識頻道 <a href=\"https://t.me/twittermansyunzou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwittermansyunzou&d=m%2FBV6vIUiVByATU953YnmDIStCm0mHK7%2Bbmf%2BnNiY0c%3D&h=bf9f57f5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/twittermansyunzou</a><br />\n7. 不要說推，試著copy and paste呢段嘢<br />\n8. 保持<span style=\"color: red;\">獨立思考</span>，分析能力level up，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">冷處理fake news/ rumour</span></strong> 、五毛分化post<br />\n<br />\n<em>每星期任務：</em><br />\n1. <span style=\"color: red;\">低消費</span>，高儲蓄；罷買Bye Buy Day：星期日、星期五(唔買非必需品）<br />\n2. <span style=\"color: red;\">做孝子救港</span>，關心下老母老豆老人家，自己老母自己救<br />\n3. 去<span style=\"color: red;\">連儂牆</span>貼3張文宣，輸出革命思想<br />\n<br />\n<em>每月任務：</em><br />\n1. 出糧換美金、買美股，MPF都買美股<br />\n2. 搵多一個人參與<br />\n3. 關心社會、陪審員、派傳單、放映會<br />\n或者做唔足，但我會堅持到尾；Best effort，你呢？<br />\nVersion 2019.09.13 @Template End@"},{"pid":"7240c0423c0604febfabd20cd78b8e29824c4c1e","tid":1564704,"uid":207462,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T01:48:24.000Z","msg":"政府今次誠信完全破產<br />\n你點宣傳都冇用<br />\n日撚日播埋嗰個珍惜香港嘅廣告有撚用<br />\n都係得垃圾藍絲同港豬會理你<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc4064b340ae4a4b22a3b7cb25d046128123f147","tid":1564704,"uid":212238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T01:49:31.000Z","msg":"冰封三尺<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9387ca4c7d8ee2bf6d6e8df9f462812abaa8741f","tid":1564704,"uid":48667,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T01:50:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>林鄭當時提到，宣傳工作為港府最薄弱一環（I dare not say government carries out propaganda, but at least in terms of dissemination of factual information we are very, very weak），稱若能度過言這場危機，必須進行大改革，為繼任人營造較好管治環境，又自爆有國際公關為免被拖累名聲而請特區政府食檸檬。<br />\n<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nOn9, 係改革先會平息,<br />\n唔係平息左先改革呀屌你老母"},{"pid":"5573b5926ec05662321c4cbf118f9d3babea8de5","tid":1564704,"uid":170229,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"70ca641fe45f0620605a77be4503b6156866a153","tid":1564704,"uid":144492,"like":88,"dislike":0,"score":88,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T01:46:10.000Z","msg":"我反而覺得佢而家係用緊呢個錄音<br />\n放緊啲潛台詞嚟影響外國判斷<br />\n「佢只有3萬警察」<br />\n嚟掩蓋支那武警已混入嘅事實<br />\n「被國際公司請食檸檬 文宣弱」<br />\n「有人認為佢對示威者無