na.cx/i/ch4X7sO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fch4X7sO.jpg&h=971c9013&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GNTfvwM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGNTfvwM.jpg&h=6cb0c505&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z1DfvwN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz1DfvwN.jpg&h=6f8fb244&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2riOQwO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2riOQwO.jpg&h=074cd595&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uCaEXbO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuCaEXbO.jpg&h=0736be80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n每日任務：<br />\n1. 抵制支持「邪惡」「無良」的商店，例如cctvb廣告、黨鐵商埸、黑社會、打壓員工的店鋪，減少淘寶、減少八達通<br />\n2. 安全情況下跳閘，免費搭港鐵<br />\n3. 夜晚十點吶喊！！！<br />\n4. 做運動，身體健康，鬥長命<br />\n4. 每日一個post，社交媒體戰（Twitter, IG, Facebook, Reddit) #HongKongProtest<br />\n#FreeHongKong #HongKongProtests #Chinazi<br />\nTwitter 共識頻道 <a href=\"https://t.me/twittermansyunzou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwittermansyunzou&d=m%2FBV6vIUiVByATU953YnmDIStCm0mHK7%2Bbmf%2BnNiY0c%3D&h=bf9f57f5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/twittermansyunzou</a><br />\n5. 不要說推，試著copy and paste呢段嘢<br />\n6. 保持獨立思考，分析能力level up，抵抗fake news/ rumour <br />\n<br />\n每星期任務：<br />\n1. 罷買Bye Buy Day：星期日、星期五(唔買非必需品）<br />\n2. 做孝子救港，關心下老母老豆老人家，自己老母自己救<br />\n3. 去連儂牆貼3張文宣<br />\n<br />\n每月任務：<br />\n1. 出糧換美金、買美股<br />\n2. MPF都買美股<br />\n3. 搵多幾個人參與<br />\n或者做唔足，但我會堅持到尾，Best effort，你呢？<br />\nVersion 2019.09.06"},{"pid":"dc088b5a0502d68dbc7780da3396e2beda6a2dbe","tid":1564704,"uid":171866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1684e5bdf97535e291a8a8181ce9885610123126","tid":1564704,"uid":289565,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"70ca641fe45f0620605a77be4503b6156866a153","tid":1564704,"uid":144492,"like":88,"dislike":0,"score":88,"citedBy":5,"r